{"analytics_identifier":"OT1333","base_path":"/government/organisations/modernisation-and-reform","content_id":"2d6316c6-3826-4263-a28c-931cead9b852","description":"We are committed to working towards the common purpose of reforming government and modernising the Civil Service to better deliver for the public. Modernisation and Reform is part of the Cabinet Office .","details":{"acronym":"","alternative_format_contact_email":"csmr-engagement@cabinetoffice.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>We are committed to working towards the common purpose of reforming government and modernising the Civil Service to better deliver for the public.</p>\n\n<p>Modernisation and Reform is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/cabinet-office\">Cabinet Office</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"cabinet-office","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Modernisation and Reform"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/john-glen-sets-out-plan-for-modern-civil-service-to-deliver-stronger-public-services","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/65afb036bc0de30013187339/s712_John_Glen_GOVUK.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/65afb0363348490012c73934/s465_John_Glen_GOVUK.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/65afb036bc0de3001318733a/John_Glen_GOVUK.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2024-01-22T22:30:06.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>In his keynote address at the Institute for Government’s annual conference, the Minister for the Cabinet Office, John Glen, will outline his long-term priorities to modernise the Civil Service into a more productive institution so it can deliver stronger public services</p>\n</div>","title":"John Glen sets out plan for modern Civil Service to deliver stronger public services"},{"document_typ